286
00:13:45,135 --> 00:13:45,894
Zhang Jinbao!

287
00:13:46,295 --> 00:13:46,734
Master,

288
00:13:46,975 --> 00:13:47,854
I've wronged you.

289
00:13:48,255 --> 00:13:48,854
I've wronged you.

290
00:13:48,895 --> 00:13:50,014
Zhang Jinbao,

291
00:13:51,455 --> 00:13:52,894
