292
00:13:54,495 --> 00:13:56,134
What a mess.

293
00:13:57,335 --> 00:13:57,854
Matriarch!

294
00:13:58,455 --> 00:13:58,974
Matriarch!

295
00:14:04,095 --> 00:14:06,014
This is just an appetizer.

296
00:14:06,975 --> 00:14:08,254
You'll pay the heaviest price

297
00:14:08,895 --> 00:14:10,534
for your crimes.

298
00:14:14,615 --> 00:14:15,294
Ms. Ye,

299
00:14:16,015 --> 00:14:16,974
you just reported a suspect

300
00:14:16,975 --> 00:14:17,694
at the Zhou residence

301
00:14:17,695 --> 00:14:19,374
linked to two murder cases.

302
00:14:19,695 --> 00:14:20,214
Where is she?

303
00:14:20,335 --> 00:14:21,014
That's her.

304
00:14:22,055 --> 00:14:22,934
Four years ago,

305
00:14:23,215 --> 00:14:24,854
Nanxi forged Chuxue's handwriting

306
00:14:25,135 --> 00:14:26,294
to invite the Steward Xu Hansheng

307
00:14:26,615 --> 00:14:28,054
to a secret meeting in the garden.

308
00:14:28,855 --> 00:14:29,814
This led to Chuxue

309
00:14:30,455 --> 00:14:31,934
being sexually assaulted by the Steward.

310
00:14:34,095 --> 00:14:35,494
And ultimately drowning mysteriously.

311
00:14:36,455 --> 00:14:37,454
Several months ago,

312
00:14:38,055 --> 00:14:39,294
Zhou Residence's Third Concubine

313
00:14:39,695 --> 00:14:41,254
was framed as a suicide.

314
00:14:42,615 --> 00:14:44,694
The handwriting in her suicide note

315
00:14:45,655 --> 00:14:47,774
is identical to the letter from Chuxue

316
00:14:47,935 --> 00:14:49,934
four years ago in writing habits.

317
00:14:50,375 --> 00:14:51,974
This is the evidence I've collected this year

318
00:14:52,015 --> 00:14:53,974
linking Nanxi to two murder cases.

319
00:14:54,535 --> 00:14:56,774
This handwriting is completely different

320
00:14:57,415 --> 00:14:58,534
from mine, though.

321
00:14:58,535 --> 00:15:00,494
It's different from your right hand's writing.

322
00:15:00,775 --> 00:15:01,934
But have you forgotten?

323
00:15:02,375 --> 00:15:04,294
The consent form you signed

324
00:15:04,295 --> 00:15:05,334
at the hospital was left-handed.

325
00:15:10,575 --> 00:15:11,654
Where's the doctor?

326
00:15:12,855 --> 00:15:14,054
No matter what happens,

327
00:15:14,695 --> 00:15:17,174
please help me keep the baby.

328
00:15:19,695 --> 00:15:20,694
It hurts.

329
00:15:21,055 --> 00:15:22,094
What are you doing?

330
00:15:22,335 --> 00:15:23,454
This is to protect the baby.

331
00:15:23,935 --> 00:15:24,894
Don't worry.

332
00:15:28,095 --> 00:15:28,734
Okay.

333
00:15:29,815 --> 00:15:30,414
Okay.

334
00:15:31,575 --> 00:15:32,214
Miss Nanxi,

335
00:15:32,375 --> 00:15:33,094
before the surgery,

336
00:15:33,095 --> 00:15:35,054
we need you to sign a consent form.

337
00:15:40,975 --> 00:15:41,814
My hand...

338
00:15:43,095 --> 00:15:43,974
My right hand...

339
00:15:45,935 --> 00:15:47,334
Why can't I move my right hand?

340
00:15:47,335 --> 00:15:48,014
Use your left hand.

341
00:15:48,015 --> 00:15:48,494
Quickly!

342
00:15:48,575 --> 00:15:50,134
Otherwise the doctor can't proceed.

343
00:16:05,695 --> 00:16:06,614
That day I instructed the nurse

344
00:16:06,615 --> 00:16:08,214
to inject anesthetic into your right hand.

345
00:16:09,175 --> 00:16:09,774
The purpose was to obtain

346
00:16:10,615 --> 00:16:13,334
evidence of your left-handed writing.

347
00:16:15,935 --> 00:16:17,814
You're such a treacherous woman.

348
00:16:20,215 --> 00:16:21,614
I never claimed

349
00:16:22,175 --> 00:16:23,534
to be a good person.

350
00:16:27,095 --> 00:16:28,294
Alright, Miss Nanxi.

351
00:16:28,735 --> 00:16:30,294
You're now suspected of two murders.

352
00:16:30,295 --> 00:16:31,294
Come with us to the station

353
00:16:31,295 --> 00:16:32,174
for investigation.

354
00:16:35,415 --> 00:16:36,094
Let go of me!

355
00:16:37,015 --> 00:16:38,494
Let go! I'll walk myself.

356
00:16:44,295 --> 00:16:45,374
Take care of the child.

357
00:16:47,175 --> 00:16:48,254
Our child.

358
00:16:50,455 --> 00:16:51,694
Zhang Jinbao.

359
00:16:53,015 --> 00:16:53,534
Get out!

360
00:16:54,095 --> 00:16:54,534
Yes.
